{
  "stem": "10181.4",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were so left-- left alone, you know, so we went back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went looking for my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I noticed there were some young children together in the-- in her same-- in the same barracks as she was, you know, like me, young-- young boys, so I wanted to be moved to be together with her.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she wanted me to be together with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a while, we succeeded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they-- they agreed that I could stay with her, you know, with-- which was a barracks of women, actually.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for the first few weeks, except for the lack of food and the lack of sanitation-- this really was the-- the worst part.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Each barrack had sort of a washroom attached to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was a tap.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no showers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't take a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a wash room with a few taps and cold water, which wasn't always there, and you had to go-- if you wanted to go to the toilet, you had to go to, like, an outhouse, further away.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's all there was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, that's the sanitary conditions we had in Bergen-Belsen at the beginning, but it wasn't too crowded at first.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we got there, the only other people in our city-- the camp was divided into several sections.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In our section was a new section, which originally was called the-- the-- it was called a [GERMAN], which means the-- the camp with the stars because we were wearing the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were wearing our own clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The rest of the camp were wearing those striped pajamas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were wearing our own clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And originally, this-- this was considered to be an exchange camp, like I said.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
